{"tid":1221744,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發］必睇！野餐/戶外活動防曬裝備！","createTime":"2019-06-14T09:33:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T12:18:54.000Z","uid":198369,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"5e9e4024c10d475718faefa79bae9072e69513ff","tid":1221744,"uid":198369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T09:33:09.000Z","msg":"話說我發夢見到自己呢一兩個禮拜會成日去野餐<br />\n咁啲太陽好勁㗎嘛 同時有可能會有狗狗亂噴嘢 掟嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以我都想買返個面罩眼罩保護下自己<br />\n不過呢啲裝備偏貴 又唔係好多地方有<br />\n物資站雖然有好多 但係都唔夠咁多野餐人士用<br />\n大家可以考慮下買大媽帽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4atBJ0b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4atBJ0b.png&h=d5339e6a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bBxu30c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbBxu30c.png&h=c6e384a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n平平哋 而且好多地方都有得買<br />\n平時可以防UV遮下太陽 狗狗癲起上嚟可以kum住自己塊面<br />\n胡椒噴霧射唔到眼 射bb彈都（應該）擋到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係感動彈啲煙霧就應該擋唔到<br />\n所以可以加返個口罩<br />\n琴日睇post有巴打介紹pitta牌子口罩，濕咗水後可以阻煙霧<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Bty6mQH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBty6mQH.png&h=30cda01f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n然後再安全啲可以按低塊遮光罩然後戴個頭盔<br />\n咁就算啲狗狗周圍掟嘢都會安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n（利申：大媽帽當然唔及眼罩/全面罩安全啦，但係勝在比較易買同平，between無啦啦俾狗搜身搵到大媽帽都容易解釋過防毒面具<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n純屬意見 不喜勿插<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要插就16號一齊出維園打鳩我啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n野餐最緊要安全 自己香港自己救！！"},{"pid":"c95ceae873e257a3228bc8dadc2bcbbbbbcb915f","tid":1221744,"uid":198369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T09:40:57.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"b9b8d0763f7a49dd52f04d0d15f56667bcabbe07","tid":1221744,"uid":198369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T10:04:10.000Z","msg":"Post錯台sorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5cc24ea80d08f789e9aa5d768f2a3f7dca585d9","tid":1221744,"uid":198369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T12:18:54.000Z","msg":"Pushhhhh"}]}